Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:06.36,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,無聊 真無聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.76,0:00:08.38,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.80,0:00:12.26,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我知道啦 只要說服老爺子就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.80,0:00:16.92,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,讓他同意GHQ施行的財閥解体政策
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.44,0:00:20.74,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,要不要一些涼飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.40,0:00:21.80,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.70,0:00:34.90,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,誰都不會違抗我命令的世界 真是無聊又沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.72,0:00:38.12,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,但是這樣才有離開的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:40.82,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,拋棄這個家的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.66,0:00:49.54,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,飛鳥 飛鳥 你醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.76,0:00:52.44,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,嗯 醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.32,0:00:59.58,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,早上好 春日部 還有莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.36,0:01:01.54,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.98,0:01:03.26,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,飛鳥 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.96,0:01:21.02,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,明明沒必要陪著我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.70,0:01:25.04,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不過他也算在努力做好一個頭領啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.26,0:01:30.06,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,十六夜君！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.52,0:01:33.08,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊 大小姐 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.96,0:01:37.00,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,給我起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.38,0:01:46.04,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,哇 仁君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:52.24,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,喂喂 大小姐啊 一上來就這麼玩會死人的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:54.66,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,緊急狀況 你看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:02:12.06,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,火龍誕生祭？北邊的美術工藝品展示會和評價會 由各種各樣的人舉辦的恩惠遊戲 主要比賽是由階層支配者舉辦的大會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.26,0:02:17.74,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,混帳 這不是很有趣麼 不去玩玩麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:19.34,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,興致真高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:21.42,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼弄到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.38,0:02:24.56,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,黑兔好像故意把這個藏起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.14,0:02:27.38,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,春日部碰巧發現了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:28.88,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,碰巧而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.46,0:02:31.72,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,是麼 保密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.70,0:02:39.50,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不 不能去啊 你覺得從這裡到北面的境界壁要多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.98,0:02:45.14,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,居然對我們隱藏這麼有趣的祭典 哭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:50.34,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,一直為了共同體努力過來了 真是杯具 哭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.86,0:02:56.88,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,看來我們有必要讓黑兔他們嘗點苦頭了 哭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:02:57.86,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:00.66,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那個……你們有在聽麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:10.82,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,至黑兔 我們要去參加北面和東面境界壁的火龍誕生祭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:14.28,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,作為隱瞞祭典的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:20.20,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,今天如果抓不住我們的話 我們就退出組織
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.52,0:03:21.62,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,拼命來找我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.94,0:03:29.24,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,這群問題兒童們！
Comment: 0,0:03:30.28,0:03:30.58,mondaiji zhengwen,,0,0,0,,OP
